Flight Management System

Actors:-
- User
- System
- Admin


Story Points for MVP
- User can register
- User can search the availability of flights based on source and destinations
- user can choose the  direct or connecting flights
- User can choose the seating class
- User can book multiple flights at scheduled times
- user can see the travel history


Advanced Story Points
- user can cancel the flight
- user can carry the luggage
- user can filter the search results based on params like time, seats, flight
- User can pay the amount
- user can put multiple stop points with different date and times;

Logic Building
- find the connecting flights [ we can use the directed graph and then find all the paths between source
  and destination. once we get all the paths can filter them out on the basis of associated cost, stops etc. ]

Doubt
- does a flight can have multiple pickup points
